name: Soul Gypsy
description: Nowadays Ventriloquy is a Sport. Who's the Dummy? Split the Difference. A Frayed Knot Knows the Runner. She Can't Escape Herself for Long. Daisy Does Push-Ups but Finds no Resting Peace. It's Hard Not to Watch but Don't Get Sucked in. She's a Soul Gypsy and She'd Gladly Sacrifice Yours for Hers. Temporary Relief Comes at a High Price. Avoid at all Cost.
